window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A sham marriage to an infamous playboy - what could possibly go wrong? Don’t miss the breathtaking, high-stakes conclusion to the Dirty Games duet by </b><b><i>New York Times</i></b><b> best-selling author Laurelin Paige!</b></p> <p>Their union started with a simple plan: to fake a marriage that would allow Elizabeth to take over her father’s company and merge it with Weston’s holdings, creating a vast media empire. But what began as a pretend marriage has become all too real....</p> <p>Now a bombshell about Weston’s past is keeping him rooted at home while Elizabeth must travel across the globe to take up the company reigns. But their intense connection could bring the entire game crashing down as they’re forced to choose power and family...or the love of a lifetime.</p>"; 
